[{'action': 'opened', 'author': 'wu-sheng', 'comment_id': None, 'datetime': '2016-11-06T06:51:49Z', 'masked_author': 'username_0', 'text': '- As I mentioned before in #149, I am translating OpenTracing Documents to Simplified Chinese version . 

