 {'action': 'created', 'author': 'bensigelman', 'comment_id': 260150298.0, 'datetime': '2016-11-12 21:43:01+00:00', 'masked_author': 'username_1', 'text': "@username_0 sorry for the delay here, I had a crazy week.

